The air permit application (APEN) for the the turbine power unit exchange for 
the La Plata C/S was submitted to the state of Colorado.  

A meeting was attended with Southwest Gas and PG&E in Las Vegas concerning 
PG&E's forthcoming media statement which it will distribute to the selected 
sectors of the public informing them of the discovery of PCB's received from 
Transwestern.  Southwest Gas is a customer of PG&E.  PG&E and Southwest Gas 
have jointly agreed to conduct sampling activities on the Southwest Gas 
system to determine presence and extent of possible PCB contamination on the 
Southwest system.

Attended the cross functional training meeting in Albuquerque.